  "comment": "LED Ellipsoidal • 20-bit color mixing through 6 colors: Red, Green, Blue, Cyan, Lime, Amber • All whites from 2700 to 10.000 K with  CRI>95 • 16 bit dimming electronics with 4 selectable curves (exponential, logarithmic, linear and halo) digitally processed at 20 bit • Flicker-free operation • Fan setting with 4 different options (low, studio, auto, DMX regulated) • PowerCon True 1 In & out panel mounted connectors • XLR 5 Pin DMX In & out panel mounted connectors • Remote Device Management (RDM) • Max power consumption: 220 W • Built In Power Supply 90-250V 50/60Hz Autosensing •  2 mt. detachable Blue POWERCON True1 power cable with bare ends • Size: 362x214x210 mm (without optic) • Weight (with Profile zoom 15°-35° optic): 11 kg • Weight (with lens tube 19° optic): 9.5 kg",
